  "texts": [
    "It is also important that the now higher number of heavy users have opportunities to share techniques and best practices they have discovered with their less experienced peers.",
    "Universities will play an important role in guiding their communities through this transition to a period of both increased and well-reflected AI use.",
    "When asked to evaluate their university's response to generative AI in spring 2024, most interviewees were reasonably satisfied.",
    "Ultimately, interviewee satisfaction with their institution's response was tied to seeing indications that their university was reacting proactively.",
    "Interviewees appreciated messaging from senior leadership and the existence of task forces, committees, and workshops, which made them feel, as one language professor put it, \"like I am in good hands.\""
